</node>
<node id="Putin">
  <data key="d0">Putin</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Putin is a political figure whose actions in other parts of the world affect energy bills for families and businesses in the UK, according to UK Prime Minister Keir Starmer.&lt;SEP&gt;Putin is a political leader referenced as having various servants including Prigozhin, Roldugin, Kovalchuk, Timchenko, and the Rotenberg brothers.&lt;SEP&gt;Putin is a person whose critique is described as primitive and unserious in the source text.&lt;SEP&gt;Putin is the leader of Russia who has alliance obligations with North Korea, fulfilled by North Korean troop deployment.&lt;SEP&gt;Putin is the Russian leader whom the survey respondents believe should be pressured to cease fire.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bba75e995cd78b326b3a8504ee463aff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-02f8127f57647c6f52ac2f580f293f65&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84aafb35212f27429824f947049d3e74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec36c3f34e874fb6a0c44b533c707cfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ed06713c000461ec66858856eef1a63</data>
