<node id="Starlink">
  <data key="d0">Starlink</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Starlink is a satellite internet service provider whose disconnection allegedly reduced the effectiveness of Russian FPV drone operators.&lt;SEP&gt;A satellite internet service provided by SpaceX, used by Russian forces.&lt;SEP&gt;Starlink is a satellite internet service that the U.S. offered to provide to Cuba in exchange for reforms.</data>
