<node id="Armed Forces of Ukraine (AFU)">
  <data key="d0">Armed Forces of Ukraine (AFU)</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">The Armed Forces of Ukraine are the Ukrainian military, which is using advanced radio technical reconnaissance to target Russian drone operators.&lt;SEP&gt;Armed Forces of Ukraine (AFU) is the military of Ukraine, reported to have suffered 1.5 million casualties and to be facing an inevitable defense collapse.</data>
