  <data key="d0">Razvedos</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Razvedos is a pro-Russian source who notes that Ukrainian forces are systematically targeting Russian drone operators.&lt;SEP&gt;Razvedos is the call sign of Alexander Arutyunyan, a Z-blogger who commented on the Russian army's capabilities.</data>
