<node id="France">
  <data key="d0">France</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">France is a European NATO member state that operates Falcon 8X Archange intelligence aircraft.&lt;SEP&gt;France is a country that is part of the E3 and other smaller EU meeting formats.&lt;SEP&gt;France is the country where Marine Le Pen holds political office.&lt;SEP&gt;France is a country where far-right parties close to Russia are forced to criticize Donald Trump.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7d8dc136c80cd91ef2cf9ad9756a4d52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aeeb3e654a660cb7b38dfc9d61222bc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8109eafe35c828056622b31d32cb9a3b</data>
