<node id="Germany">
  <data key="d0">Germany</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Germany is a central European country and a member of both the European Union (EU) and NATO. Within the EU, Germany is part of the E3 group and participates in other smaller EU meeting formats. As a NATO member state, it operates Pegasus intelligence aircraft. The country is a prominent member of the European Union that has expressed opposition to Ukraine’s accelerated EU accession, and its Chancellor maintains sanctions on Russian oil, a policy reflected in domestic fuel prices where the price of petrol has been cited as 800 forints per liter. Germany is also the country represented by the eurodeputy Manfred Weber in the European Parliament, and it is the country to which Dietmar Clodo was extradited to face legal charges. The Chancellor of Germany is Friedrich Merz.

Germany is the home base of the far-right political party AfD, which has been involved in nepotism scandals. The country is also where far-right parties close to Russia are forced to criticize Donald Trump. Additionally, the Atomwaffen Division was active in Germany, and between the pandemic and 2025, 37 cases were identified and prevented in the country. Germany was the subject of an Insa survey assessing public opinion on aid to Ukraine, and its citizens were surveyed about a proposal involving Bundeswehr soldiers in Ukraine. The country is also referenced in the context of a video comparison, and the AfD party operates within its borders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7d8dc136c80cd91ef2cf9ad9756a4d52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce845ea082895ffef253ac499ba46794&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3117b3a03ff471f00f67b26aade3e091&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3dc55aad4eb94544269bbfd9dec2905&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ed06713c000461ec66858856eef1a63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b328e8d4304c0d0b1c17749a4f9e42bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52970e012540831e77e393d5b4e7bd3f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-786e4ab2b6966bcfcf341c317a1d4e1c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a74d8a7ca84ed003e119ba5cde1f80dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdde8f24aa613c9ae76329db019d6d7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ee2064130371330ef4a5652dba192c2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed3f829c79f231e6cf23a14022015c5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8109eafe35c828056622b31d32cb9a3b</data>
