  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Belarus is a country that shares a border with Poland, where the "Eastern Shield" fortifications are being built.&lt;SEP&gt;Belarus is a country Russia uses to drive migrants towards Europe.&lt;SEP&gt;Belarus is a country cited as a stark example of the long-term consequences of falling under Russian influence.</data>
