<node id="Speaker">
  <data key="d0">Speaker</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The speaker is the individual who created the video, requested information about CNC machines at Russian defense enterprises, and offers exclusive content on Patreon, YouTube sponsorship, and Telegram Channel "Bytili Plus".&lt;SEP&gt;A noticeable individual, 171 cm tall and weighing 122 kg with 2% body fat, who delivered money and items to various people, including Dietmar Clodo and Victor Shander Pinter.&lt;SEP&gt;The speaker is the main narrator who was in a coma, did not initially identify their assailant to police, and later discusses criminal connections in Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Speaker is an unidentified person who expressed a negative opinion.</data>
