  <data key="d2">Latvia is a Baltic country where Russia could create a narrative of oppression of Russian speakers.&lt;SEP&gt;Latvia is a country that refused to allow Robert Fico's plane to fly over its territory.&lt;SEP&gt;Latvia is one of the Baltic states whose ministers informed Robert Fico's office that they would not allow his plane through their airspace.</data>
