<node id="Peter Pellegrini">
  <data key="d0">Peter Pellegrini</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Peter Pellegrini is the President of Slovakia and a former Prime Minister, facing a decision about a referendum.&lt;SEP&gt;Peter Pellegrini is the leader of the pro-Russian HLAS-SD party.&lt;SEP&gt;Peter Pellegrini is a Slovak politician, a former prime minister who ordered F-16 jets in 2018, and the current president of Slovakia.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-11b9d96fc698fa7b9242168a7bad3295&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d2e8519cd0bab60a3e52b70a90d3f0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0db27d1e5bd672959a82744488e5a07</data>
