  <data key="d2">The Slovak National Party was part of the government coalition that supported Fico against the no-confidence vote.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovak National Party is a political party led by Andrej Danko that failed to pass the parliamentary threshold.&lt;SEP&gt;The Slovak National Party is a political organization previously in a coalition with Robert Fico.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovak National Party is a political party that formed a coalition with Robert Fico, as mentioned in the source text.</data>
