<node id="Slovakia">
  <data key="d0">Slovakia</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Slovakia is a Central European country that has been the setting for a series of notable political events and foreign policy stances. The nation has faced allegations of foreign interference in its electoral processes, with claims that the Kremlin and Hungary allegedly interfered in Slovak elections. It is also the country where Viktor Orbán allegedly directed illegal migrants to create a migration crisis. Domestically, a treason investigation has been launched against the country's Prime Minister, Robert Fico, who has led the nation through periods of significant geopolitical tension and is currently changing the electoral code. The country is experiencing prolonged political, budget, and economic crises, and its government's stability has been questioned after Viktor Orban's defeat. Slovakia is also the country of citizenship for Yozef Rogoch, and it issued a life sentence against Rogach.

In foreign policy, Slovakia has taken distinct and often contradictory positions. Prime Minister Robert Fico stated that the country will not support the 20th EU sanctions package against Russia. Working alongside Hungary, Slovakia has actively blocked EU sanctions, secured a delay on voting for sanctions, and sought an exception to continue buying Russian gas and oil. The two countries have threatened to block the extension of EU sanctions, and Slovakia has been suspected of leaking information to Moscow. Together with Hungary, Slovakia prepared a proposal for the EU regarding the sanctions removal of Ismailova, and the two countries received an exception from the European Union in 2022 to continue importing Russian oil. Furthermore, Prime Minister Fico is seeking an alternate flight route to Moscow, and the country has refused to participate in a European Union credit for Ukraine.

Conversely, in military and energy affairs, Slovakia has demonstrated support for Ukraine by donating MiG-29 fighter jets to Ukraine in 2023 and ordered F-16 fighter jets as a replacement for its fleet. However, in a contradictory move, Slovakia has also announced a similar decision to halt diesel exports to Ukraine and is struggling to restore the Druzhba pipeline. The country, which receives oil transit via the Druzhba Pipeline, disputes damage to that pipeline from a Russian strike and did not condemn Russia for the attack. Slovakia is expected to receive resumed Russian oil supplies via the Druzhba pipeline, and it is also a country mentioned as a potential recipient of oil products from Croatia. Its markets receive gas supply via the Adriatic Pipeline. Prime Minister Fico has negotiated with Ukraine's president on EU integration and bilateral relations, but the government decided to terminate the emergency power supply contract with Ukraine. Slovakia is a country bordering Ukraine where criminal groups have operated, and it is also affected by the alleged Ukrainian oil blockade. Under Prime Minister Robert Fico, along with the US under Trump, Slovakia is portrayed as sharing Viktor Orbán's stance on Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovakia is a country where far-right parties close to Russia are forced to criticize Donald Trump.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-11b9d96fc698fa7b9242168a7bad3295&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d2e8519cd0bab60a3e52b70a90d3f0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fe37316c34f12bcbc2eaa45277e7b90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bde507aa2566c6c22d3e526f2ec971df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b346b60f2318d240edb84608cb2b374&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6610955fc2b94d091c65e9f7449d2028&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0db27d1e5bd672959a82744488e5a07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69d93e1cd4546542fd7a6dd43a3e688d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc1feb8e698e39594612de628b9b30f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-204b60f8b5f56bb209e8ca6cc9af48f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09de750ab096b64385f95a95c7d0e5ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cab9a94ea286a7616cc63009e8c3d5ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-313fbd5b1968d3d281c042524d458b06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9bcca043358a8f1b8a9a2999a79a6f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f6038412dae5ce5c36860aae0893cce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac57a8e21b0821ebfc4b7007fb6688a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-116374b92e94e5c9f902ad74ec9408ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c252425b51c0e430a65f3fb6d91f843&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-141360bcc1e8268affe7476ca1b210ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3889b30c247676595bbcc845df96d9ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2842b9c04cc247c5969a9739ff25b33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3dc55aad4eb94544269bbfd9dec2905&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e84aa583f7aa058a2cdc38864b8c765a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9d4541f93fbe1abbecc6f52128db7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8109eafe35c828056622b31d32cb9a3b</data>
