<node id="Israel">
  <data key="d0">Israel</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Israel is a country that has been involved in various international and regional matters. Hungarian Foreign Minister Szijjártó has mentioned Israel as a partner, indicating diplomatic communication between the two. The country is also the current residence of Leonid Tyura. In September 2024, Israel conducted a deadly attack targeting Hezbollah's pagers. Israel has been involved in a conflict described as a meaningless war against Iran, alongside the United States. Additionally, secret documents related to Israel detailed the activities of Semen Mogilevich. Regarding the Gaza conflict, the Israeli government's actions received unconditional support from Ursula Von Der Leyen, a stance that drew criticism from far-left factions. Furthermore, Israel's actions in the Gaza conflict became a point of criticism against the position of the European Commission.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-efac8eca24c7251212c13175865647fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f7b78146485b6ecfc5184d01e665fc8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-204b60f8b5f56bb209e8ca6cc9af48f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8f1d70c706294695eca41aa0252d062&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a73e41ce47973ce6d0501f8f7acc0955</data>
