  <data key="d2">Serbia is a country whose partners are mentioned as being in communication with Hungarian Foreign Minister Szijjártó.&lt;SEP&gt;Serbia is mentioned as a partner with whom Szijjarto communicates.&lt;SEP&gt;Serbia is the country whose media described Dmytro Kornienko as an ultra-nationalist radical.&lt;SEP&gt;Serbia is the country where Aleksandar Vučić serves as President.</data>
