<node id="Orban">
  <data key="d0">Orban</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Orban is the Hungarian prime minister described as a Kremlin agent in the source text.&lt;SEP&gt;Orban is a political figure whose role is referenced as something another actor is not ready to assume.&lt;SEP&gt;Orban is a political figure who made statements about the risks of Ukraine's EU membership.&lt;SEP&gt;Orban is a political figure whose political technologists are described as creating separatist agitation banners.</data>
