<node id="Szijjarto">
  <data key="d0">Szijjarto</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Szijjarto is the Hungarian Minister of Foreign Affairs who claimed he communicated with ministers from multiple countries, but only called the Kremlin during toilet breaks.&lt;SEP&gt;Szijjarto is a pro-Putin politician who visited Moscow 16 times during the war and acts as a contact for Sergei Lavrov.</data>
