  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Lavrov is the Russian Minister of Foreign Affairs who received reports from Szijjarto.&lt;SEP&gt;Lavrov is a Russian official who gave instructions and requested a document regarding Ukraine's EU accession negotiations.&lt;SEP&gt;Lavrov is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Russia, involved in phone conversations with Hungarian officials.</data>
