<node id="Progressive Slovakia">
  <data key="d0">Progressive Slovakia</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Progressive Slovakia is a political party alleged to be a spoiler party in Slovak elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Progressive Slovakia is a pro-Western political party in Slovakia.&lt;SEP&gt;Progressive Slovakia is a political party currently leading in ratings and is a potential ally for opposition parties.</data>
