<node id="The Washington Post">
  <data key="d0">The Washington Post</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Washington Post confirmed accusations that Szijjarto leaked confidential information.&lt;SEP&gt;The Washington Post is a media organization that reported on the conversation between Hungarian and Iranian officials.&lt;SEP&gt;The Washington Post is a newspaper that saw the internal SVR report about the "Gamechanger" strategy.&lt;SEP&gt;The Washington Post is a newspaper that reported on the SVR RF documents regarding the proposed operation.</data>
