<node id="Politico">
  <data key="d0">Politico</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">POLITICO is a media organization that published Zelenskyy's statements.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico confirmed that Brussels excluded Hungary but delayed official accusations.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico is the publication that obtained documents showing the agreements between Hungary and Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico is a media organization that reported on the exclusion of Hungary from EU discussions.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico is a news organization that reported the allegations against the AfD.</data>
