<node id="Druzhba Pipeline">
  <data key="d0">Druzhba Pipeline</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The Druzhba Pipeline is a major oil pipeline used for transporting Russian oil. It serves as a critical infrastructure route through which Russia supplies oil to Hungary and Slovakia. The pipeline has been the subject of multiple geopolitical actions, including Ukraine halting the transit of Russian oil through it, which led to Slovakia's refusal to support the 20th EU sanctions package. Additionally, the pipeline was reportedly blocked by Ukraine, prompting Slovakia and Hungary to urge for its restoration. In a separate incident, the Druzhba Pipeline was shelled by Russia, which resulted in the halting of emergency electricity supplies to Ukraine. Furthermore, the pipeline was allegedly damaged by a Russian strike on January 27.&lt;SEP&gt;The Druzhba Pipeline is the oil pipeline through which Hungary demands the restoration of oil supplies.&lt;SEP&gt;The Druzhba Pipeline is an oil pipeline whose potential repair and resumption of supplies is a central point of political conflict between Ukraine and Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Druzhba Pipeline is an oil pipeline whose operation was blocked by Ukraine, leading to Hungary's seizure of Ukrainian funds.&lt;SEP&gt;The Druzhba Pipeline is an oil pipeline whose Ukrainian section was damaged by a Russian strike on January 27.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0d2e8519cd0bab60a3e52b70a90d3f0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fe37316c34f12bcbc2eaa45277e7b90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc1feb8e698e39594612de628b9b30f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-204b60f8b5f56bb209e8ca6cc9af48f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b80d70d8670ebee7e64e3613a75c65de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c252425b51c0e430a65f3fb6d91f843&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-870499425ae897e4d4a7fe9c0c2b515c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-141360bcc1e8268affe7476ca1b210ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf3c850f2801bc7e22334b0ebc4ddaab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-febe32c9e0da364a16a64ecb34a3ae7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21313de66f58c55ed37fed59c551bfe8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9d4541f93fbe1abbecc6f52128db7e</data>
