<node id="Republican Party">
  <data key="d0">Republican Party</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Republican Party is a US political party whose infrastructure Viktor Orban reportedly used to form his political style.&lt;SEP&gt;The Republican Party is a political party in the United States, of which Don Bacon is a member and which is still present in the US.</data>
