<node id="Brussels">
  <data key="d0">Brussels</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Brussels is the capital city of Belgium and serves as the administrative center of the European Union, frequently functioning as a metonym for the EU's institutions in political discourse. In the context of Hungarian politics, Brussels is a central symbolic location, often referenced in the rhetoric of Prime Minister Viktor Orbán. Orbán has portrayed Brussels as an imperial dictator and a direct threat, accusing it of attempting to interfere in Hungarian elections and of wanting to draw Hungary into a war. The city is also identified as the source of decisions concerning Hungary, such as the freezing of funds. Furthermore, the term is used to describe a political entity that figures like Peter Magyar are not aligned with, a characterization that Orbán has exploited by attempting to cast Magyar as an agent of Brussels. Consequently, narratives from certain political perspectives frame the future of Brussels as being dependent on the outcome of Hungarian elections, with a specific waiting period noted until April 12.&lt;SEP&gt;Brussels is the location where new data regarding Ukraine's financial situation has originated from.&lt;SEP&gt;Brussels is a location referenced as the source of control for Péter Magyar in the disinformation campaign.&lt;SEP&gt;Brussels is the location of the European Commission, criticized by Orban for maintaining sanctions.&lt;SEP&gt;Brussels is the administrative center of the European Union, subject to demands from Kyiv.&lt;SEP&gt;Brussels is the de facto capital of the European Union, used as a term to represent the EU; the Russian strategy aims to portray Peter Magyar as its puppet.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-791a0f308fdc4f1a500e850db6490862&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd0a283b39238236a064e8afb069c87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4089c9c991c6402b317d88ca6848ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49d9496e943d94ccc071cf105396b990&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84aafb35212f27429824f947049d3e74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1d344e42d77e1e71d20f49e3f03482d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-febe32c9e0da364a16a64ecb34a3ae7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3960e17c128f750dfd948945c91a00ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3dc55aad4eb94544269bbfd9dec2905&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f26cc7528a3ccfcc5b72d2752bd95332&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-583ccb318ed3bd5eb71b569940315d4f</data>
  <data key="d4">C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\110.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\124.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\16.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\27.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\53.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\59.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\72.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\9.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\95.txt</data>
