<node id="Felcsut">
  <data key="d0">Felcsut</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Felcsut is a village in Hungary where Viktor Orban built a large stadium, symbolizing the fusion of his personal power, sport, and politics.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3</data>
