  <data key="d2">Dmytro Kornienko is a Ukrainian political scientist, founder of Resurgam, described by Hungarian propaganda as an ultra-nationalist radical, influential personality in Ukraine, personal friend of Volodymyr Zelenskyy, and gray cardinal of Ukrainian information policy.</data>
