<node id="Volodymyr Zelenskyy">
  <data key="d0">Volodymyr Zelenskyy</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Volodymyr Zelenskyy is the President of Ukraine. As a Ukrainian politician, he has been involved in various domestic and international political matters. He has made statements regarding European unity and internal disagreements. Zelenskyy has been the subject of claims from Hungarian propaganda, which has alleged that Dmytro Kornienko personally supports him. Hungarian Prime Minister Viktor Orbán has claimed that Zelenskyy was intentionally not repairing a pipeline, and has also attempted to frame him as having ties to Peter Magyar. Additionally, Hungary has accused Zelenskyy of blackmail.

In the realm of diplomacy and conflict resolution, Zelenskyy believes that negotiations with Russian President Vladimir Putin are necessary. He has also conducted negotiations with the Prime Minister of Slovakia and had a conversation with Slovak Prime Minister Robert Fico.&lt;SEP&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy is a person who reported on Croatia's readiness to supply oil products and commented on Orban's reluctance to purchase.&lt;SEP&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy is a foreign leader who was demanded by Péter Magyar to apologize before ties between the European Union and Ukraine could be restored.&lt;SEP&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy is the president of another country, targeted by campaign demonization in Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy is the President of Ukraine, accused by Orban of maintaining an oil blockade against Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy is a leader addressed alongside Ukrainians by Viktor Orban.&lt;SEP&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy is a person for whom the Istanbul Agreement would have been a better peace solution than current discussions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c4fcaac079096c59954da324c3f17538&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49d9496e943d94ccc071cf105396b990&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78d9923aabbca45b70bc35cbb1701e26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3117b3a03ff471f00f67b26aade3e091&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac57a8e21b0821ebfc4b7007fb6688a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-116374b92e94e5c9f902ad74ec9408ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf3c850f2801bc7e22334b0ebc4ddaab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3889b30c247676595bbcc845df96d9ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-713408326a31f030b9c00f6efef043ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d3ef991a8152469dff039e1e39a042bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3dc55aad4eb94544269bbfd9dec2905&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a55dfa4e37443ca4a575c4564e64f2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74413fdb4ad3f1b0bd542a794fe97eaa</data>
