  <data key="d2">Péter Szijjártó is the Hungarian Foreign Minister who Dmytro Kornienko claims serves under Sergey Lavrov.&lt;SEP&gt;Péter Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary, who communicates with Russian officials and is described as acting on behalf of Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Péter Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary, accused of destroying documents.&lt;SEP&gt;Péter Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary who made the statement about blocking the sanctions.</data>
