  <data key="d0">Sergey Lavrov</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sergey Lavrov is the Russian Foreign Minister, under whom Dmytro Kornienko claims Péter Szijjártó serves.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is the Russian Foreign Minister who discussed EU documents with the Hungarian Foreign Minister.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is a Russian official who had a series of leaked conversations with Peter Szijjarto.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is a Russian official whose conversations with Peter Szijjarto have been leaked.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is the Russian Foreign Minister who received live reports from Hungarian officials during EU meetings.</data>
