<node id="18th Sanctions Package">
  <data key="d0">18th Sanctions Package</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The 18th Sanctions Package is a set of sanctions adopted by the European Union that targeted Russian companies and banks, and was resisted by Peter Szijjarto.</data>
