<node id="Петер Сийярто">
  <data key="d0">Петер Сийярто</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Петер Сийярто is a Hungarian politician who spoke with Сергей Лавров and commented on surveillance and sanctions policy.&lt;SEP&gt;Петер Сийярто is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary who called for the lifting of sanctions on Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Петер Сийярто is the Hungarian Minister of Foreign Affairs who is alleged to have transmitted data from EU meetings to Moscow.</data>
