  <data key="d2">Сергей Лавров is a Russian politician who had a conversation with Петер Сийярто.&lt;SEP&gt;Сергей Лавров is the recipient of a proposal to send EU documents via the Hungarian embassy in Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Сергей Лавров is the Russian Foreign Minister who allegedly received confidential data from EU meetings via Петер Сийярто.</data>
