<node id="Венгрия">
  <data key="d0">Венгрия</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Hungary, also referred to by its Russian name Венгрия, is a Central European country with complex geopolitical and cultural characteristics. The nation is largely pro-Western, demonstrating high levels of public support for its membership in both the European Union and NATO, and it conducted elections on April 12. The country is where the events described in various narratives took place, serving as the setting for a story involving the narrator and Alexander Kirichanin, who emigrated there in 1994, as well as the location for specific localities such as the village of Bócsal and its associated election.

Despite its Western alliances, Hungary’s energy security and interests are frequently referenced in the context of sanctions policy, as it remains significantly dependent on Russian energy supplies. This reliance has led to a continued interest in maintaining dialogue with Russia, a stance that has put it at odds with other powers. Consequently, Hungary has been described by Russian official Dmitry Peskov as an unfriendly country. Nonetheless, within the country itself, there are reports of celebration and national festivities.&lt;SEP&gt;Hungary is a country that allowed Роберт Фицо to fly over on his way to the parade the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;Венгрия is the country that Петер Сийярто represents as foreign minister.&lt;SEP&gt;Hungary, the country whose government launched the petition.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f4398c1136d9d0745f3589421281ecc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de92df91fd68b8019a5e2c98e87d545e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51df0a094ef10ee7cc34dc0f7c1bf5c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca3f7ffc74cdedb95fe34f9bf520fbf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07b6315bf58723ab4516f38303c600bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77680239477915203c692473a1450584&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81f9a312226a282bf8ebf1aee5ad788a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74724c9370b40962ccf8e0ef74c5dbf6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1cf1470bc49240f9597eaaea1f12646e</data>
