  <data key="d0">Ministry Of Foreign Affairs Of Ukraine</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Ukraine is the government body of Ukraine that reported on the mistreatment of Ukrainian detainees in Budapest.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Ukraine is the state organization that launched the "Hungarian Radio of Ukraine" project.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Ukraine is a government body that confirmed the location of the unlawfully detained Oschadbank vehicles in Hungary.</data>
