<node id="Donald Tusk">
  <data key="d0">Donald Tusk</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Donald Tusk is a Polish politician whose statement about Donald Trump's actions benefiting Russia was responded to by Viktor Orban.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Tusk is the Polish prime minister who reacted to the leaked transcript of Orbán and Putin's conversation by publicly questioning Orbán's actions.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Tusk is the Prime Minister of Poland, who commented on the Szijjártó leak.</data>
