  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Kirill Dmitriev is a special representative of Vladimir Putin who praised Viktor Orban's stance on the energy and economic crisis.&lt;SEP&gt;Kirill Dmitriev is a Russian official who was involved in leaked negotiations with Steve Witkoff and Yuri Ushakov.</data>
