  <data key="d0">Szilveszter Pálinkás</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Szilveszter Pálinkás is a former captain in the Hungarian army who studied with Gáspár Orbán at the Royal Military Academy Sandhurst and revealed details of the Chad mission plans.</data>
