  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Bloomberg is a media organization that published a record of a telephone conversation between Viktor Orban and Vladimir Putin.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is an organization that obtained and published the transcript of the Orban-Putin call.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is a news organization that published satellite images showing an empty reservoir at the Brody oil depot.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is a news organization that reported on the protest against Viktor Orban's policies.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is the publication that reported the information about North Korea's military aid to Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is a news organization that reported on the reassessment of ties between European far-right parties and Donald Trump, and provided a photograph of Greenland.</data>
