<node id="JD Vance">
  <data key="d0">JD Vance</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">JD Vance is an American political figure who stated that Ukrainian special services contain elements attempting to influence elections in the United States and Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;JD Vance is an individual who informed Donald Trump that approximately 5,000 Hungarian patriots were on the line during a phone call.&lt;SEP&gt;JD Vance is a person who visited Hungary to support Viktor Orban before the elections.&lt;SEP&gt;JD Vance is the US Vice President who visited Budapest to campaign for Viktor Orban.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8be82194b3f8b4851149bcd5709c9f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84d9d2605d4824a81c0829b9eb92d7b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a810084503e65cb067ff1fc3c7a05189&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4219648b35dcbd430c607633467c92dc</data>
