<node id="Igor Korol">
  <data key="d0">Igor Korol</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Igor Korol is a crime boss and leader of an organized crime group in Hungary who tried to extort Laszlo Koch.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol is a person involved in criminal circles, known as a figure with authority who sought to address a violent incident involving a mother of three.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol is a person whom István Hoffmann approached for protection payments and for whom the speaker translated.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol is a person involved in collecting money and acting as an intermediary, working with Semyon Mogilevich.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol was a close friend and associate of the witness, involved in the criminal group.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol is a person who was not allowed back into Hungary after deportation.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol was the leader of a Ukrainian criminal group in Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
