<node id="Semyon Mogilevich">
  <data key="d0">Semyon Mogilevich</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Semyon Mogilevich, also referred to as Seva, is a central figure in organized crime, involved in large-scale financial operations and business schemes.&lt;SEP&gt;A person who believed his situation improved after Arbanc came to power and who was described as rude and insulting. He was a sponsor of Arbanc.&lt;SEP&gt;Semyon Mogilevich is a person of Jewish origin, a key figure in organized crime, who paid money to police and political figures for influence.&lt;SEP&gt;Semyon Mogilevich was a high-ranking boss in the criminal hierarchy in Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
