<node id="Igor">
  <data key="d0">Igor</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Igor is an individual who was in a close relationship with the speaker and with whom the speaker discussed the bombing event.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor is a person who was provoked by the speaker, known to have killed people for a quarter of what was said to him, apologized repeatedly, and attempted to transfer money to Bucharest for casino investments before being deported from Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual with whom the speaker's relations deteriorated after the 1998 elections. He took a car from Sasha Kirichanina and demanded money from him.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1780159089</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sandor Pinter">
  <data key="d0">Sandor Pinter</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sandor Pinter is a high-ranking police official who, according to the source, ordered the murder of Boros Tomas and was responsible for the speaker's imprisonment.&lt;SEP&gt;Sandor Pinter is the former head of police in Hungary, now the Minister of the Interior of Hungary, who collaborated with Semyon Mogilevich and received bribes.&lt;SEP&gt;Sandor Pinter is a chief of police who received regular payments from Semyon Mogilevich and was known to be a person of Viktor Orban.&lt;SEP&gt;Sandor Pinter is a person who came to power with Viktor Orban, became Minister of Interior, and cracked down on criminal world figures he previously associated with.&lt;SEP&gt;Sandor Pinter is the current Minister of Internal Affairs of Hungary and was the Chief of Police of Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
  <data key="d4">C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1780159508</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Mogilevich">
  <data key="d0">Mogilevich</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Mogilevich is a person who had connections with Viktor Orban and others, as described in Boros Tomas's recorded confession.&lt;SEP&gt;Mogilevich is a person who was involved in transferring money to a king.&lt;SEP&gt;Mogilevich is a person who was forced to leave Hungary and moved to Russia, possessing compromising material on Viktor Orban.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
