<node id="Hungarian Police">
  <data key="d0">Hungarian Police</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Hungarian police are the law enforcement agency that managed the speaker's imprisonment and likely employed the interrogators.&lt;SEP&gt;Hungarian Police listened to phone conversations between the speaker and Igor, leading to Igor's deportation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
