  <data key="d0">István Hoffmann</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">István Hoffmann was the first associate of József Prisztás; he was later bombed but survived with burns.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e</data>
