</node>
<node id="Dietmar Clodo">
  <data key="d0">Dietmar Clodo</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">A German of Jewish origin who was involved in the manufacture of explosive substances and was convicted by a Hungarian court.&lt;SEP&gt;Dietmar Clodo is a person who lived in Szentendre and received money deliveries from the speaker.&lt;SEP&gt;Dietmar Clodo was a key agent of Semen Mogilevich in Budapest as a former mercenary in Rhodesia and Afghanistan. He was convicted for a series of bombings in Hungary and extradited to Germany to face charges of murder, bank robbery, and other serious crimes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
  <data key="d4">C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1780159508</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
