</node>
<node id="Seva">
  <data key="d0">Seva</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Seva is a person who acted as an intermediary and arbitrator in disputes between Igor Korol and Leonid Stitsyura, protecting Stitsyura from reprisals.&lt;SEP&gt;Seva is a person whose office the speaker could only access accompanied by Igor Korol.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
