</node>
<node id="Alexander Kirichanin">
  <data key="d0">Alexander Kirichanin</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alexander Kirichanin is Laszlo Koch's childhood friend who moved to Hungary with him and was involved in the vodka business.&lt;SEP&gt;Alexander Kirichanin is a person described as a friend and involved in a conflict with Igor Korol related to the speaker's childhood home.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
