  <data key="d0">Александр Киричанин</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Александр Киричанин is a businessman, a childhood friend of the narrator, who emigrated to Hungary in 1994 and was involved in the vodka business.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868</data>
