  <data key="d0">Будапешт</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The city where the narrator experienced a life-threatening medical emergency and traffic jams.&lt;SEP&gt;Budapest is the city near which the town of Budaörs is located.&lt;SEP&gt;Будапешт is the city where the meeting at Октогон took place.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
