  <data key="d0">Будоверш (Budaörs)</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Budaörs is a town near Budapest where Alexander Kirichanin was assaulted and robbed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868</data>
