</node>
<node id="Пинтер">
  <data key="d0">Пинтер</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Пинтер is a person referenced by the narrator in a threat, suggesting he would be among the first to go to prison.&lt;SEP&gt;Пинтер is a person who helped negotiate to prevent Игорь Король from being convicted.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d</data>
