  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Hungarian government was accused of high treason by the opposition.&lt;SEP&gt;The Hungarian Government signed an agreement with Russia to expand economic, trade, energy, and cultural ties.&lt;SEP&gt;The Hungarian Government controls private media and uses state propaganda to create hostility towards Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;The Hungarian government banned the entry of three Ukrainian citizens, accusing them of threats.</data>
