  <data key="d0">Виктор Орбан</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Виктор Орбан is the Prime Minister of Hungary whose minister made a proposal described in the text.&lt;SEP&gt;Виктор Орбан is the Hungarian Prime Minister who built his political career as a mouse serving a Lion, and faces elections on April 12.&lt;SEP&gt;Виктор Орбан is a leader whose regime is described as a "Trojan horse" inside the European Union and NATO, systematically distancing Hungary from these organizations and relying on Russian influence.&lt;SEP&gt;Виктор Орбан is a politician who suffered a defeat, as noted in the source text.&lt;SEP&gt;Виктор Орбан is a Hungarian politician referenced in the context of the diesel export halt.&lt;SEP&gt;Виктор Орбан is the recipient of the open letter written by Виктор Ющенко.</data>
