<node id="VSquare">
  <data key="d0">VSquare</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Vsquare is a center for international investigations in Eastern Europe that reported on Operation Budapest.&lt;SEP&gt;VSquare is the source that reported on Lavrov giving instructions to Szijjarto.&lt;SEP&gt;VSquare is a media organization that published the leaked conversation along with other outlets.&lt;SEP&gt;VSquare is a journalistic investigation project that collaborated with European security services to uncover Russian interference in Hungarian elections.&lt;SEP&gt;VSquare is a Hungarian publication that conducted a previous investigation confirmed by the arrival of Russian military intelligence operatives.&lt;SEP&gt;VSquare is a Polish-Hungarian investigative group that reported on Russian military intelligence operatives arriving in Hungary.</data>
