  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Croatia is a country, and its minister commented on the deal; Croatia also plays a supporting role in the described events.&lt;SEP&gt;Croatia is a country used as a comparison for the cost of highway construction.&lt;SEP&gt;Croatia is a country through which energy supplies could be diversified, an option Viktor Orban refused.&lt;SEP&gt;Croatia is a country from which Hungary refuses alternative oil supplies.&lt;SEP&gt;Croatia is a country that expressed readiness to supply oil products to Slovakia and Hungary.</data>
