<node id="MOL">
  <data key="d0">MOL</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">MOL is a major Hungarian oil company whose operating profit increased during the war, and over 30% is owned by funds affiliated with Viktor Orban.&lt;SEP&gt;MOL is a Hungarian oil company and a monopolist on the domestic fuel market, receiving Russian oil via the Druzhba pipeline at a price significantly lower than the global market price.</data>
