  <data key="d0">Moldova</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Moldova is a country where a previous operation by Kiriyenko's team failed.&lt;SEP&gt;Moldova is a country where Russia attempted to influence elections through vote buying and information campaigns.&lt;SEP&gt;Moldova is a country where Russian interference attempted to prevent the re-election of Maia Sandu and prevent the pro-European party from winning the parliament.&lt;SEP&gt;Moldova is a country where similar Russian operations reportedly took place.&lt;SEP&gt;Moldova is a country where Kiriyenko's operatives previously ran vote-buying and disinformation networks against pro-Western President Maia Sandu.&lt;SEP&gt;Moldova is a country where the spoiler candidate technology, associated with Kremlin political technologists, became entrenched.&lt;SEP&gt;Moldova is a country that is modernizing its energy system to reduce its dependence on Russian energy.</data>
