<node id="AfD">
  <data key="d0">AfD</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Alternative for Germany (AfD, also referred to as АдГ or АДН in some texts) is a German far-right political party. The party is currently led by Alice Weidel and has been the subject of significant criticism from political figures such as Friedrich Merz. The AfD is known for its strong Eurosceptic and pro-Russian stance; a large portion of its voters largely reject any aid to Ukraine, and the party has been suspected of leaking European Union secret documents to Russia. Notable members include Björn Höcke (Бьорн Хёке), who is described as a convinced pro-Russian member.

The party has been involved in multiple scandals, including allegations of nepotism and the preferential employment of relatives at both state and federal levels. Furthermore, some members of the AfD have been linked to the far-right extremist group Atomwaffen Division, and have been arrested during raids in Germany. In certain descriptions, the party has been derogatorily referred to as a "hunched dog with a fake mane," reflecting the intense political criticism it faces.&lt;SEP&gt;AfD is a political party in Germany whose supporters strongly oppose the idea of deploying Bundeswehr soldiers in Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;AfD is a German right-wing political party led by Alice Weidel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-de92df91fd68b8019a5e2c98e87d545e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ed06713c000461ec66858856eef1a63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b328e8d4304c0d0b1c17749a4f9e42bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52970e012540831e77e393d5b4e7bd3f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74413fdb4ad3f1b0bd542a794fe97eaa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a74d8a7ca84ed003e119ba5cde1f80dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdde8f24aa613c9ae76329db019d6d7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c748c9a23ba05cffbc5245984ffc52e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ee2064130371330ef4a5652dba192c2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed3f829c79f231e6cf23a14022015c5c</data>
  <data key="d4">C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\12.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\13.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\14.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\15.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\19.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\22.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\27.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\3.txt&lt;SEP&gt;C:\WikiRag\RAG-GeoSpoiler\GeoSpoiler-RAG-Hybrid\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\8.txt</data>
