<node id="Oschadbank">
  <data key="d0">Oschadbank</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Oschadbank is a Ukrainian state bank whose cash convoy was detained and confiscated by Hungarian authorities.&lt;SEP&gt;Oschadbank is a Ukrainian bank that reported the hijacking of its employees, cash-in-transit vehicles, and valuables in Hungary on March 5, 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;Oschadbank is a Ukrainian bank. Seven of its cash collectors were involved in an incident in Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Oschadbank is a Ukrainian bank from which cash and gold bullion were stolen in an operation targeting its cash collectors.&lt;SEP&gt;Oschadbank is a Ukrainian bank whose money and valuables were placed under arrest according to the proposed bill.&lt;SEP&gt;Oschadbank is a Ukrainian bank from which funds were seized from collectors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04a007153cdf32c13e7e322795fc37d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-350a5144d8e2787035e85988d9818a16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6a8f4f06a47d67e1f0a25d123d913f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-769ff8feb3b00c3c503fb9e86e9bdf0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c99964a997545fd96cbae2fac33e426b</data>
