<node id="János Lázár">
  <data key="d0">János Lázár</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">János Lázár is the Hungarian Minister of Construction and Transport who stated that Hungary would not return the seized Ukrainian money and gold, treating it as collateral.&lt;SEP&gt;János Lázár is the Minister of Construction and Transport of Hungary who publicly admitted to the seizure of Ukrainian funds and threatened further operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21313de66f58c55ed37fed59c551bfe8</data>
