  <data key="d0">Raiffeisen Bank</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Raiffeisen Bank is a bank in Vienna that was sending a cash transfer to Oschadbank in Kyiv.&lt;SEP&gt;Raiffeisen Bank is an Austrian bank that had an international agreement with Oschadbank for the transport of foreign currency and bank metals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04a007153cdf32c13e7e322795fc37d0</data>
