<node id="European Commission">
  <data key="d0">European Commission</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The European Commission is a European Union institution accused by Robert Fico of reaching record levels of incompetence and ideological blindness.&lt;SEP&gt;European Commission is the EU body that started an investigation into espionage by Hungary in October 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;The European Commission is the executive branch of the European Union, led by President Ursula Von Der Leyen.&lt;SEP&gt;European Commission is the executive branch of the European Union, whose entire composition is forced to resign if a motion of censure is adopted.</data>
