<node id="European Parliament">
  <data key="d0">European Parliament</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The European Parliament is the parliamentary institution of the European Union mentioned in the context of awarding "green" projects.&lt;SEP&gt;European Parliament is the EU institution where the first accusations of Hungary spying for Russia were made in January 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;The European Parliament is the legislative body of the European Union where far-right and far-left factions initiated no-confidence motions against Ursula Von Der Leyen.&lt;SEP&gt;European Parliament is the legislative body where motions of censure are initiated and voted upon.</data>
