  <data key="d0">1956 Hungarian Uprising</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The 1956 Hungarian Uprising was an anti-Soviet revolt in Hungary, brutally suppressed by Soviet troops with tanks, and the origin of the slogan "Russians go home!".&lt;SEP&gt;1956 Hungarian Uprising was a suppressed revolt in Hungary, remembered as a source of anti-Russian sentiment.</data>
