<node id="Semen Mogilevich">
  <data key="d0">Semen Mogilevich</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Semen Mogilevich is a Russian mafia figure known as the "Brainy Don" with a state estimated at over $10 billion. He controlled military and defense companies in Hungary and had a stake in Russian-Ukrainian energy trade. He was convicted in Russia for tax evasion.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
