<node id="Al-Qaeda">
  <data key="d0">Al-Qaeda</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Al-Qaeda is a terrorist organization to which Semen Mogilevich's organization allegedly sold weapons.&lt;SEP&gt;Al-Qaeda is a jihadist organization that was allegedly financed by Al-Taqwa Bank and sought alliances with white supremacist groups.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c0e45973e2056f2a0c6c6cf9df17553</data>
