<node id="FSB">
  <data key="d0">FSB</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The FSB is the Russian security service that received compromising videos of Viktor Orban from Semen Mogilevich in 2008.&lt;SEP&gt;FSB is a Russian security service. The source text questions whether Viktor Orban is an FSB agent.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ccbba289defe85bee861c66ae67de11</data>
