<node id="Hungarian Electoral System">
  <data key="d0">Hungarian Electoral System</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The Hungarian electoral system is a unique mixed proportional-majority system where the majority and proportional components function as "communicating vessels" that interact, not as independent components.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8c1110bd39ddbd2f60dff21ab98ff641</data>
