  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Hungarian Parliament is the legislative body where seats are allocated based on the Hungarian electoral system.&lt;SEP&gt;Hungarian Parliament is the legislative body of Hungary that will vote on a temporary confiscation law.</data>
