  <data key="d2">Tisa Party is a political party led by Maďar that is expected to gain a majority in the parliamentary party list section and likely a majority in the parliament.&lt;SEP&gt;Tisa Party is a political party led by Peter Magyar, which has a potential 20% lead among decided voters.&lt;SEP&gt;Tisa Party is a Hungarian opposition party whose members were targeted by Russian disinformation campaigns.</data>
