  <data key="d0">90 Billion Loan</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The 90 Billion Loan is a financial instrument from the European Union that Ukraine was initially expected to require by early April but now has sufficient funds to delay its receipt until the end of April.</data>
