<node id="North Korea">
  <data key="d0">North Korea</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">North Korea, officially known as the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, is a country in East Asia under the leadership of Kim Jong Un. The nation possesses nuclear forces and is the base of operations for Kim Jong Un and his daughter, who is also associated with the country. North Korea has become deeply involved in the war in Ukraine through significant military cooperation with Russia, which includes its leader expressing support for Russia's invasion of Ukraine and calling on youth to prepare for war on Russia's side. This cooperation has involved deploying thousands of soldiers to Russia to participate in the conflict against Ukraine as part of a foreign special operation. Reports indicate that North Korea dispatched over 10,000 soldiers to Russia, with specific estimates suggesting that about 14,000 soldiers were sent in 2024 alone. The country reportedly uses the war as a training ground for its army through regular troop rotations, with some soldiers becoming instructors after gaining combat experience.

Additionally, North Korea is increasing military cargo shipments to Russia, supplying ammunition and other military equipment in exchange for key military technologies and improved economic conditions from Russian orders. The country's military assistance to Russia has been substantial, valued at up to $14.4 billion from August 2023 to December 2025, encompassing both weapons and troops. North Korea's missile production department is a key element of this overall military support effort. In return, the country benefits from Russian orders, effectively acting as a factory for Russia, which has led to improved conditions for the nation. The soldiers sent from North Korea are being memorialized in cases of death, as the country opened a memorial complex dedicated to its soldiers, highlighting the human cost of this military cooperation. North Korea has also participated in negotiations with a Russian delegation regarding this partnership.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korea is a country that held a concert as described in the source text.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1769d39ef03a8083db256740e9cd0766&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec36c3f34e874fb6a0c44b533c707cfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f539231f0337d24e0f7782691b6fac00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce8f15f650ac7d354598ceb3c44ee55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-939a2cfef1695d968a321a56df325c53&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c81a93a3b90360d5428ecf518612acfc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2cd9eaecb1b87407745fb11b4c0a1b5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8262c667cbee1913092248cf832b5b2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe4a537b10e5a1cd6b9731ae8a2ee0a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22bf377cf0305c3d3989c37e5d3450cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc8a59662338ae99506795bdf8f3e570&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bea54a7e2da99c4d21fe120e09b5930&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b081d06450863ed7e420f49361e136e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1c5a44337225374fecdeb2a9881ccb4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f525f78f89f5b96d8fc7535b3303ae6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-214c05e5837b1920019322b383e38e60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a32816fdb3610e6d8a54bb67883ce674&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef573f6547db918e0c04e9db6d87c22b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7c66fd004b5169922bcb617129ac236&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-407b20f30b0250ff3bfa0029af7e723c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-182d3ae7e14d1083d21cb4dce15639d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fc30f8f11256ef823b68dfe69edd994&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a8abc972632e3037cdcfe65da8e68da</data>
