<node id="North Korean Soldiers">
  <data key="d0">North Korean Soldiers</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">North Korean Soldiers are the soldiers who died in battles against Ukraine and are being memorialized by a monument and museum.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korean soldiers involved in artillery strikes against Ukraine, drone reconnaissance, mine clearing in Kursk Oblast, construction work, and personnel rotations. Some have become instructors in North Korea after gaining combat experience.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korean Soldiers, numbering over 10,000, were sent to Russia and are being deployed to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korean soldiers are military personnel who were killed in the war against Ukraine, and their graves were the subject of the landscaping order.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1769d39ef03a8083db256740e9cd0766&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f539231f0337d24e0f7782691b6fac00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-939a2cfef1695d968a321a56df325c53&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a32816fdb3610e6d8a54bb67883ce674</data>
