  <data key="d0">North Korean Troops</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">North Korean troops are military personnel from North Korea deployed to Russia, participating in combat operations against Ukrainian border settlements under Russian command, and are involved in conducting aerial and artillery reconnaissance, as well as fire adjustment.</data>
