  <data key="d0">Kursk Oblast</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Kursk Oblast is a region in Russia where North Korean troops are directly involved in combat operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Kursk Oblast is a location in Russia where North Korean soldiers are involved in mine clearing operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Kursk Oblast is a region in Russia mentioned in connection with fallen North Korean soldiers.&lt;SEP&gt;Kursk Oblast is a location in Russia where North Korean soldiers died.&lt;SEP&gt;Kursk Oblast is a location where mercenaries of the Korean People's Army were eliminated.</data>
