<node id="Pyongyang">
  <data key="d0">Pyongyang</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Pyongyang is the capital of North Korea, which uses the war in Ukraine as a training ground for its army.&lt;SEP&gt;Pyongyang is the capital city of North Korea where the new residential complex was opened.&lt;SEP&gt;Pyongyang is the capital city of North Korea where the propaganda march took place.&lt;SEP&gt;Pyongyang is a location that supplied artillery pieces to Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Pyongyang is the capital of North Korea, used metonymically to refer to the North Korean government that expressed support for Russia's invasion.&lt;SEP&gt;Pyongyang is the capital of North Korea where the Youth League congress was held.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec36c3f34e874fb6a0c44b533c707cfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2cd9eaecb1b87407745fb11b4c0a1b5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc8a59662338ae99506795bdf8f3e570&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bea54a7e2da99c4d21fe120e09b5930&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-407b20f30b0250ff3bfa0029af7e723c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-182d3ae7e14d1083d21cb4dce15639d9</data>
