  <data key="d2">Korean People's Army is the military force of North Korea that celebrated its 78th founding anniversary.&lt;SEP&gt;Korean People's Army is the military force of North Korea, whose young soldiers are described as participating in foreign operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Korean People's Army is a military organization whose mercenaries were eliminated in Kursk Oblast.</data>
