  <data key="d2">КНДР, also known as North Korea, is a country that participated in negotiations with a Russian delegation and has sent troops and weapons to support Russia in the war against Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;КНДР is a country, also referred to as North Korea, whose pharmaceutical companies are planning to supply drugs to Russia.</data>
