  <data key="d2">Ursula von der Leyen is a person who co-signed a joint statement with Antonio Costa regarding the plan.&lt;SEP&gt;Ursula von der Leyen is the President of the second European Commission, which faced a wave of motions of censure between 2025 and 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;Ursula Von Der Leyen is the President of the European Commission and a representative of the European People's Party, making her a central figure in the European political establishment targeted by both far-right and far-left factions.</data>
