  <data key="d0">Patriots For Europe</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Patriots for Europe is a far-right political group in the European Parliament that initiated motions of censure in October 2025 and January 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;Patriots For Europe is a far-right political faction in the European Parliament that criticizes Ursula Von Der Leyen.</data>
