  <data key="d2">White jihad is a term describing the current trend of white supremacist neo-Nazi movements adopting jihadist ideologies and tactics, particularly originating from the United States.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4c0e45973e2056f2a0c6c6cf9df17553</data>
