  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">David Myatt is a British neo-Nazi and Islamist, author of works such as "A Practical Guide to Aryan Revolution" and "Are Martyrdom Operations Lawful According to the Qur’an and Sunnah?", whose ideas were promoted by Aryan Nations.</data>
