<edge source="European Union" target="Slovakia">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Slovakia, under Robert Fico, declared it would not support the 20th EU sanctions package due to the Ukraine pipeline blockage.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovakia and Hungary secured a delay in voting and threatened to block the extension of EU sanctions in order to demand the removal of Russian individuals from the list.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovakia refuses to participate in the European Union's 90 billion euro credit for Ukraine.</data>
