<edge source="European Union" target="Viktor Orban">
  <data key="d7">10.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between Viktor Orban and the European Union is characterized by a long-standing and deep conflict. Orban’s policies and actions frequently contradict European standards and norms, leading him to be described as a major destructive factor within the bloc. A key point of contention is Hungary's blocking power, which Orban has used to undermine collective EU efforts, particularly regarding support for Ukraine. This includes sabotaging a proposed 90 billion euro loan and opposing the EU's plan to use frozen Russian assets, which he labeled a new level of escalation.

Orban often frames these conflicts as a struggle against what he views as an imperialistic EU bureaucracy. He accuses the European Union of interfering in Hungarian elections and has indirectly criticized EU bureaucrats by praising the alternative stance of lifting sanctions. While he has supported the EU’s proposed fact-finding mission, his overall posture is one of opposition, with his government's policies repeatedly found to be at odds with European Union principles.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban's election campaign is built on anti-European propaganda.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban promotes the idea that European taxpayer money disappears in Ukraine instead of helping Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d9">accusation,conflict,criticism,destabilization,diplomatic mission,disagreement,hostility,opposition,policy conflict,propaganda,relationship,rhetoric,sabotage,support,threat</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9aedd80ca30611f4314d3afe2ee2ad0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd0a283b39238236a064e8afb069c87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2369463d8ede9e477cfaf832815ef3c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1704b3bc09f596547c35a95941e29e5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1d344e42d77e1e71d20f49e3f03482d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9146ec09ad979307f3d7a3148725401&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-141360bcc1e8268affe7476ca1b210ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6a8f4f06a47d67e1f0a25d123d913f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e84aa583f7aa058a2cdc38864b8c765a</data>
