<edge source="European Union" target="Viktor Orbán">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Orbán, as a member of the European Union, discussed serving a leader engaged in a hybrid war against the EU.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán blocked the 20th EU sanctions package against Russia and a 90 billion euro EU credit to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Brussels (EU) is waiting for April 12 in response to Orbán's moves, according to the text.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán has paralyzed the European Union by blocking aid to Ukraine and key reforms.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán expresses that the EU should not join the war in Ukraine, stating it is not the EU's war.</data>
