<edge source="NATO" target="Russia">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The experience from Russia's war with Ukraine is considered possibly inapplicable in a war with NATO.&lt;SEP&gt;Russian propagandists propose capturing Narva to "break" the political will of NATO.&lt;SEP&gt;Russia warned that if NATO approached its borders, it would lead to war.&lt;SEP&gt;Russia claims NATO is preparing for confrontation and is itself preparing for a potential war with NATO.</data>
