<edge source="Ukraine" target="Viktor Orbán">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Viktor Orbán accused the crowd of wanting to give Hungarian money to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán has stated that Ukraine might attack Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán blocked European Union aid to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán stopped diesel fuel supplies to Ukraine in response to Ukraine halting Russian oil transit.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán blocked €90 billion in EU funds allocated to Ukraine for budget deficit financing.</data>
