<edge source="Russia" target="Hungary">
  <data key="d7">10.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Hungary and Russia share a complex and multifaceted relationship characterized by political friendship, economic dependency, and geopolitical tension. On the political front, Hungary has maintained a notably friendly stance toward Moscow, exemplified by the actions of Foreign Minister Peter Szijjarto and the government's pro-Moscow policies, which have drawn domestic protest and criticism. This alignment has been reinforced by an active Russian influence operation designed to support Hungarian Prime Minister Viktor Orban. Additionally, Hungary’s offer of assistance to Iran has raised further questions regarding the depth of its political ties with Russia. On the economic side, Hungary is heavily dependent on Russia for energy resources, importing 90% of its oil and 95% of its gas, largely through the Druzhba Pipeline, and also relies on Russian involvement in nuclear power plant construction. There have also been allegations that Hungarian aircraft transported cash and valuables from Russia. Geopolitically, Russia is perceived as using Hungary as a lever of influence to undermine cohesion within both the European Union and NATO, with critics arguing that Russia has no genuine interest in Hungary’s long-term well-being.&lt;SEP&gt;Hungary relies on Russia for accessible oil supply to maintain energy affordability.&lt;SEP&gt;Cheap Russian oil is described as vital for Hungary to overcome the oil crisis.</data>
  <data key="d9">dependency,diplomacy,energy dependence,energy import,energy supply,financial transfer,friendship,influence,leverage,oil trade,operation,political influence,political links,trade,transport</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e1730c3250b026b4761918dd560d02f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc1feb8e698e39594612de628b9b30f8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4089c9c991c6402b317d88ca6848ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3da3b046ca1fff9119eaf735e34f56d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f7b78146485b6ecfc5184d01e665fc8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89e09c599b4678441dbd4c330f5e7aa1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5ab60c301522fe44f5b6ce532a3c05b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-35ef5418fbb73e10428a076cc8117782&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf472d3981c26e07231b309328f0597b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3dc55aad4eb94544269bbfd9dec2905</data>
