<edge source="Vladimir Putin" target="Viktor Orban">
  <data key="d7">7.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Viktor Orban and Vladimir Putin had a phone conversation on October 17, during which they praised each other and discussed the war in Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban is described as a fan and subordinate of Vladimir Putin, voluntarily obeying him and vowing loyalty in a phone call.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban described himself as a mouse to Putin's lion in a phone conversation, reflecting his subordinate position.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban noted the very friendly tone of his conversation with Vladimir Putin and expressed a willingness to become Putin's mouse.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban is described as the main agent of Vladimir Putin within the EU.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban wrote a letter to Vladimir Putin asking about Russia's potential reaction to an EU decision on Russian assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban stated he does not consider Vladimir Putin an aggressor, disagreeing with the characterization.</data>
  <data key="d9">agent,alignment,allegiance,alliance,cooperation,correspondence,friendly relations,friendship,inquiry,loyalty,phone call,phone conversation,political disagreement,position,subordination</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ec12d27878bbf1f79c741b043b995fd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8fa6adba441e776b293e92361b9880d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd0a283b39238236a064e8afb069c87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce845ea082895ffef253ac499ba46794&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1704b3bc09f596547c35a95941e29e5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9146ec09ad979307f3d7a3148725401&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2ed677b91cd8a20441c02fa69439eac</data>
